docs.text: Introduction This repository provides a satellite rendezvous simulation following the Clohessy Whiltshire Equations. Getting Started Installations Astropy python pip install astropy def bubble_sort(items): for i in range(len(items)): for j in range(len(items) - 1 - i): if items[j] > items[j + 1]: items[j], items[j + 1] = items[j + 1], items[j] Usage this is a simple usage of hte package >>> import hello-pkg an new function
